{"id": 1770, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些为“30岁”设的门槛是有点问题的？", "description": "六十岁的童心是童心，三十岁的童心，怎么就是长不大了？", "record_count": 3818, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170629105625qNA5wUBfdF826oml.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-01T03:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 227072, "content": "各位莘莘学子，各位辛劳的妈妈们，还有各位办公室人员，不管您是哪种身份，只要您有空余的时 间，那么这份工作一定适合您【日挣100--200块钱】， 别再犹豫喽，赶快卫鑫:yy236697", "image": "img/option/option/20170803223139WnAlu92tdZkISO18", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095526}, {"id": 226561, "content": "三十岁为了买我的488，必须得把马丁卖了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094515}, {"id": 226817, "content": "30岁前要结婚。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954495}, {"id": 226563, "content": "30岁即使结婚生子了，也不要放弃对自己的修行，不要将自己定位在中年妇女或困扰在生活琐事中。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018921}, {"id": 226564, "content": "通宵一次一个礼拜恢复不过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799251}, {"id": 226565, "content": "30岁应该有车子，房子，票子，老公，孩子，公公婆婆……（?）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085495}, {"id": 226566, "content": "唉，电影都说男人四十，可现实我们三十面临婚姻，家庭，工作各种压力，中国传统逢十必庆", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094529}, {"id": 226567, "content": "给大家解释下三十而立，孔子的意思是懂礼的意思，懂得办事的道理。还有不要觉得社会给不了你可能性，是因为你本来就没什么可能性。别给自己带帽子和标签，30了就是30了，也就是个年龄而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089456}, {"id": 226568, "content": "人生就一次，不要碌碌无为。按照自己的内心去活 虽然很难 不过这是我现在三十好几的目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094536}, {"id": 226569, "content": "只要是讨论和时间有关系的就有感而发 就说明你老了或者正在变老的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094536}, {"id": 226572, "content": "坐一天就腰酸背痛，过12点睡3天也缓不过来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094561}, {"id": 226828, "content": "过了三十女人的价值就没了 就应该赶紧结婚生孩子在家做个黄脸婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094981}, {"id": 226573, "content": "30岁了就不要再做粪青了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094566}, {"id": 231181, "content": "女人30岁还没嫁出去就是剩女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107473}, {"id": 226574, "content": "30岁还这么幼稚，要成熟内敛大气内涵好嘛！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094566}, {"id": 226575, "content": "比如打游戏？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770767}, {"id": 226576, "content": "三十而立", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059247}, {"id": 226577, "content": "一切都晚了，没有时间成本，只能凑合过着无趣的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941695}, {"id": 226578, "content": "你怎么还不结婚，你咋个办哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745611}, {"id": 227858, "content": "30岁还找不到目标，事业就真的没什么前途了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022926}, {"id": 228626, "content": "抗衰老话题的前缀都是“30岁”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893693}, {"id": 227859, "content": "到了30岁，社会就会告诉你什么是现实，你的梦想也就被抹杀了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022926}, {"id": 226580, "content": "每一个都想赞一遍！这社会愚昧，迷信，盲从，固执不通的人毕竟是大多数……他们甚至凭那些陈旧观念得到了一些成就，并认为这就是铁的理论！而世界永远是年轻人的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265517}, {"id": 226581, "content": "三十岁要是还没钱，以后就这样了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094602}, {"id": 226837, "content": "中毒太深才会这样吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787171}, {"id": 234261, "content": "三十岁没结婚的女生当然没有任何错，但是别人说的也没错吧，确实难嫁了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824231}, {"id": 226582, "content": "结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530088}, {"id": 231702, "content": "其实那首歌惹的祸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 226583, "content": "没结婚就喷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094614}, {"id": 226584, "content": "30岁之后 不允许考编制内中小学教师", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258093}, {"id": 226585, "content": "30岁事业井喷，有房有车靠自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094642}, {"id": 227353, "content": "30岁之后就是剩女，特么的谁规定的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096831}, {"id": 226587, "content": "怎么还不结婚呀，都高龄产妇了呀，性取向是不是有问题……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094664}, {"id": 232475, "content": "今年28没有车，没有房 只愿人身体健康 自己活开心点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118403}, {"id": 226332, "content": "车，房，二胎，新中产", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882866}, {"id": 226588, "content": "三十而立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094661}, {"id": 226333, "content": "mark下，等我三十岁了再来答", "image": "img/option/option/20170801110837YpxRt9HiOhaunlIc.jpg", "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422542}, {"id": 227869, "content": "女人30就要结婚生子，没有结婚就被家人看成外星人 天天念经，自己的人生怎么都被插手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786224}, {"id": 226334, "content": "30岁的人生已经定型了,30岁以后社会将谋杀你所有的可能性。", "image": null, "praise_count": 261, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088568}, {"id": 226590, "content": "30 岁将到，还在飘", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094679}, {"id": 227102, "content": "最大问题被周围人催婚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096189}, {"id": 226335, "content": "30而立，凭什么要三十立，三十上有老下有小 工作竞争压力陡增。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093036}, {"id": 226591, "content": "30歲不能再當個逗比了⋯⋯⋯⋯\n30歲至少事業該有點成就⋯⋯⋯,荆棘女王奥琳娜最终承认自己是杀死乔弗里的真凶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767579}, {"id": 226336, "content": "你都长大了 怎么还。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898883}, {"id": 226592, "content": "虽然不重要，但必须要有所改变。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018444}, {"id": 226337, "content": "女孩子三十岁还不嫁人是有问题，男孩子三十岁没结婚是因为打拼事业。\r\nEXM？？？虽然我还没30岁，但我觉得这个很不OK= =", "image": null, "praise_count": 470, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789122}, {"id": 226593, "content": "三十而立", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236662}, {"id": 226338, "content": "30岁的女生 怎么就嫁不出去了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 405, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891733}, {"id": 226339, "content": "30岁至少应该年薪xxxx", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090065}, {"id": 226340, "content": "房子车子有质感的一切东西，一直的优雅美丽、已经健身5年", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698259}]}